{"tid":1790680,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"周浩鼎指「星火同盟」資金有機會用作購買「爆炸性武器」 應嚴肅跟進","createTime":"2019-12-20T07:38:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-20T13:16:01.000Z","uid":212626,"like":16,"dislike":330,"uniUserReply":119,"replies":[{"pid":"249754499f9ecbaacc23e1d3f283c956373bc344","tid":1790680,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T07:38:26.000Z","msg":"民建聯立法會議員周浩鼎認為，組織「星火同盟」成員涉嫌洗黑錢被捕，稱警方應嚴肅跟進事件。<br />\n<br />\n周浩鼎說，透過基金籌募的資金有機會支援非法暴亂，譬如是爆炸性或傷人的武器，又或為犯罪人士提供報酬。若情況屬實，有機會干犯有組織及嚴重罪行條例下的洗黑錢。同時，若組織中有人挪用資金作其他用途，則牽涉詐騙等罪行。<br />\n<br />\n周浩鼎批評有泛民議員嘗試輕描淡寫，淡化事件的法律後果，他認為事件嚴重，警方應查清資金用途。<br />\n<br />\n他又說，過往半年的非法行為背後，似乎有源源不絕的財政來源，情況引起關注，警方有責任堵截其財政來源。<br />\nttps://<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1498761-20191220.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1498761-20191220.htm&d=1CRlZafk7JeE%2BAtxbqKu5Qy7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=3cba199b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1498761-20191220.htm&h=dba1003c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1498761-20191220.htm</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1657329c76903d03f7f274dc07aff667e1128c3e","tid":1790680,"uid":242921,"like":112,"dislike":1,"score":111,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T07:39:25.000Z","msg":"有機會買套畀你屌狗呀"},{"pid":"244a76aeabbd4b23ee914a697ee43e07dade7a6a","tid":1790680,"uid":238828,"like":59,"dislike":1,"score":58,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T07:40:51.000Z","msg":"從來冇支持過你仲未死既<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70b049457e52ff3eb45001a83df5f18be8dc77de","tid":1790680,"uid":1712,"like":104,"dislike":1,"score":103,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T07:41:01.000Z","msg":"乜撚野叫有機會？<br />\n你個撚樣啲錢夠有機會用作非法用途啦<br />\n咁係咪要充公呀仆街"},{"pid":"59e0710f328c0ddafa47dd4a3f5a028e9d4